Version 1.0.0

Current Release: 1.0.0

This is the initial stable release of the Distributed Build System (DBS).

Key Features:
- Dependency management with automatic resolution and ordering
- Parallel execution of independent tasks
- Cross-platform build support
- Comprehensive logging with verbosity controls
- Build configuration validation and cycle detection
- Flexible YAML-based configuration with inheritance
- Three-phase execution system (coordination, preparation, execution)
- Conditional notifications and dependency tracking

Verbosity Levels:
- Quiet (--quiet): Minimal output
- Normal (default): Standard build output
- Verbose (--verbose): Additional information
- Debug (--debug): Detailed debug messages

